tag_line: adds the ability to make clutches hold a lot more
title: [MultiSlot Plugin] Ultra Clutches
message:
[B]This is a plugin to the MultiSlot / General ModSlot Generator, download that first for this to work:[/B]
[URL]https://www.beamng.com/resources/general-modslot-generator-multimod.31265/[/URL]

When selected in the MultiSlot Base, makes clutches a lot more durable and able to hold more power.
(Currently only works with clutches for manual transmissions)
[ATTACH]1151819[/ATTACH]
